title: Looking for Dynamic Queue partners
body: Really looking to get some new friends to play consistently with again on this game. I'm about to hit uni break so gonna be playing a lot more. I'm P5 and on a bit of a tilt streak, but can overcome it really easy. Can play decently in every role and just looking for people to chat with and play some el' classico with.

replies.body: Im gold 5 if you willing to play down here with me, i main mid and top and was a past main of support (mainly because a good friend mains that now)
